Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.66,0:00:04.95,Drifters Title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1550.134,355.101)}我的父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.66,0:00:05.20,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,把从各个村子收集到的泥土暂时存放在旧城
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.29,0:00:08.50,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不 在各村庄只要做到抽出这一步就好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.50,0:00:11.42,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,但马匹只有这些 小麦也…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.79,0:00:15.17,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么我要做这种事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.17,0:00:16.63,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.80,0:00:18.46,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,大事不好了 处男
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.46,0:00:20.76,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我的确是处男
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.55,0:00:20.72,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}大事不好了 大事不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.13,0:00:22.68,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,但别说我处男啊 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.80,0:00:24.76,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,有辆奇怪的马车在接近我们
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.31,0:00:27.31,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪的马车？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.14,0:00:33.35,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是圣日尔曼伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.65,0:00:35.77,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是奥尔特的大贵族
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.73,0:00:38.40,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,精灵族的男人快点藏起来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.40,0:00:39.28,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.94,0:00:41.45,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,女精灵不藏起来也无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.11,0:00:44.62,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.00,0:00:50.83,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,停下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.50,0:00:53.33,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,停下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.79,0:00:54.83,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,来者何人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.63,0:00:58.09,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,真是个压抑的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.09,0:01:00.21,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这个地方还真是压抑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.21,0:01:02.84,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,和想象中不同啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.84,0:01:06.30,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,想象中的是有更多闪亮闪亮 闪亮闪亮的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.30,0:01:10.27,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,在清净的森林里 和煦的阳光下 人迹罕至的神圣泉水边
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.27,0:01:13.31,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,全裸的精灵少年们和精灵们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.39,0:01:15.23,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,搞来搞去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.06,0:01:16.90,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,给我闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.77,0:01:19.23,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,圣日尔曼伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.73,0:01:23.03,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你会亲自来这样的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.11,0:01:26.03,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你是什么 漂流者么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.03,0:01:27.87,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.95,0:01:31.79,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我是旧精灵居留地的税务计算官 米尔斯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.91,0:01:34.71,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,现在被精灵们抓到…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.50,0:01:37.25,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,一股处男的臭味
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.34,0:01:39.55,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我是为了和漂流者见面而来的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.80,0:01:41.88,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,他们在这里的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.01,0:01:43.51,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,出来吧 漂流者
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.51,0:01:45.84,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊对啊 出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.89,0:01:48.47,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 男精灵也太少了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.51,0:01:51.47,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,藏起来了吧 出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.52,0:01:54.89,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,关于那个 他们现在并不在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.98,0:01:57.77,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不在是怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.86,0:02:00.65,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,他们去哪里了 你快给我一五一十地说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.78,0:02:02.15,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不然我就吃了你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.15,0:02:03.61,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,非常抱歉 非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.82,0:02:07.20,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,他们去解放矮人 然后把男精灵都带走了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.41,0:02:08.57,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 怎么说好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.66,0:02:11.24,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,去制造枪啊 机关枪什么的了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.24,0:02:11.95,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.37,0:02:13.71,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,枪…枪…枪…枪…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.75,0:02:15.96,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,居然拿去让矮人族制造
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.08,0:02:17.08,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,火…火…火…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.08,0:02:19.79,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,火药呢 火药那方面怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.84,0:02:21.34,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,火药已经有了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.38,0:02:23.05,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,已经在拼命地制造了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.26,0:02:27.14,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,完了 奥尔特完了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.14,0:02:30.25,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是叫来了何方神圣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.25,0:02:32.59,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那个小胡子已经够麻烦的了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.59,0:02:35.34,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这下可变得更加麻烦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.65,0:02:38.83,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,紫 在搞毛啊你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.83,0:02:41.88,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,搞得乱七八糟了啊混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.93,0:02:45.05,Drifters Normal,,0,0,0,,公主大人 怎么了公主大人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.07,0:02:46.43,Drifters Normal,,0,0,0,,紫…什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.56,0:02:48.19,Drifters Normal,,0,0,0,,这是我自己的事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.26,0:02:49.72,Drifters Normal,,0,0,0,,别管我了 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.24,0:02:53.19,Drifters Normal,,0,0,0,,总之在他们回来之前我就在这等着了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.32,0:02:56.68,Drifters Normal,,0,0,0,,快款待我们 盛大地款待我们
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Drifters Normal,,0,0,0,,
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Drifters Normal,,0,0,0,,---------------OP---------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Drifters Normal,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.34,0:04:33.89,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你们就是黑王及其臣下么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.51,0:04:38.89,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,居然说出 要灭亡人类 这种事情 口气还真不小啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.14,0:04:42.14,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,居然饲养 驯服隶属于我们的飞龙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.40,0:04:45.23,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,作为自己的家犬来使唤
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.73,0:04:48.23,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是在小看我们么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.53,0:04:51.24,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是黑王
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.99,0:04:54.37,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,如果想加入我们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.57,0:04:56.49,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,排到队列中便可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.53,0:05:01.62,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,面对作为青铜龙的我 竟然敢出言不逊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.12,0:05:04.50,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙算老几啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.96,0:05:08.13,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,对我来说 你是谁都没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.38,0:05:12.13,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你是什么样子或是什么种族也都无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.47,0:05:15.93,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,无论是饥饿的小哥布林还是你 都一律平等
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.18,0:05:21.02,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,给我面向这边 身披破布的白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.27,0:05:24.19,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,要我把你蹂躏成破布么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.91,0:05:40.12,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.42,0:05:49.55,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,要和我们一同前进么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.75,0:05:51.84,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,还是与他们一起迈向黄泉么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.13,0:05:54.84,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,没有旁观这个选项 青铜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.55,0:05:58.64,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,给我回答 青铜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.01,0:06:00.26,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.56,0:06:02.56,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.65,0:06:07.61,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.81,0:06:12.32,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,军团…军团算我一个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.36,0:06:15.53,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎你的加入 青铜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.99,0:06:20.99,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,现在你的姿态比起令人畏惧更多的是受人轻蔑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.20,0:06:24.21,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,拥有加入我们军团的权利
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.91,0:06:27.12,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,真是可怕的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.17,0:06:31.71,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,向来话少的你居然开口了啊 土方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.21,0:06:36.13,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我们黑王的力量是生命的增殖
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.43,0:06:39.47,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,治愈的能力也只是从中衍生出来的招数
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.55,0:06:44.98,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 无限制的增殖会生出肿瘤 直至死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.03,0:06:58.70,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不用每次都向我下跪的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.99,0:07:02.28,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我要使用力量了 你们往对面去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.42,0:07:19.43,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,只要是活物便能无尽地使其增殖
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.68,0:07:22.05,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,细胞也好 粮食也好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.47,0:07:24.85,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,对于与黑王为敌的人来说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.06,0:07:27.89,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,若以黑王作为军团指挥官来考虑的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.19,0:07:31.44,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,黑王的力量应该是噩梦般的东西了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.73,0:07:34.19,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,伤员能立即痊愈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.28,0:07:37.70,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,就连那些本来无法行动和濒死的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.95,0:07:39.99,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,也能够立马返回队伍作战
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.24,0:07:43.99,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,粮食和柴火都可以无限制地增殖
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.12,0:07:47.62,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,后勤这一概念将不复存在了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.25,0:07:50.58,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那为什么要让他们来耕作
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.88,0:07:53.96,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,食物的话 自己做出来不就好了么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.75,0:08:00.47,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因为 我并非永恒的神
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.76,0:08:04.14,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我的王
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.60,0:08:07.06,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,拉斯普京 事情办好了么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.48,0:08:10.60,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这本来就是我专业领域内的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.15,0:08:13.31,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然这不过是非常单纯的体系而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.48,0:08:16.65,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,但是再单纯一点对他们来说也比较好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.23,0:08:19.20,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,象征是眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.20,0:08:21.57,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,原型是拜火教和古老的瓦尔纳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.20,0:08:21.57,Difters PS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(747,15)}注：拜火教，基督教诞生之前中东最有影响的宗教。瓦尔纳，即印度的种姓制度。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.74,0:08:22.99,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,埃及 以及凯尔特
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.41,0:08:26.29,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,混合了其中的优点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.08,0:08:28.58,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 还有这边
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.95,0:08:31.62,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,以罗马字的基础或者说是完整照搬过来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.79,0:08:35.09,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,但是要让它们理解 还是需要时间的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.50,0:08:37.96,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你问我到底想让它们做些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.34,0:08:40.76,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是多个种族的共同体
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.01,0:08:42.76,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,狗头人 哥布林
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.18,0:08:45.60,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,今后肯定会有各种各样其他的种族加入的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.93,0:08:48.10,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,必须要施行一体化
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.43,0:08:50.14,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,创造出共通的文字
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.23,0:08:52.81,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,创立统一宗教并进行教化
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.02,0:08:57.32,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,原始农业 共通文字 统一宗教
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.53,0:08:59.78,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,一直嘲笑为怪物的他们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.90,0:09:01.82,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,将把人类代替掉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.90,0:09:04.57,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,从而在地面上诞生出文明
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.02,0:09:09.64,Drifters Normal,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.99,0:09:09.95,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.29,0:09:11.87,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你可算是醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.21,0:09:15.96,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.54,0:09:20.05,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,北壁 是龙骑兵把你救回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.09,0:09:22.09,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,吉尔德莱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.93,0:09:25.05,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,死了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.68,0:09:27.72,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,化成了盐块
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.60,0:09:30.72,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你打算要干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.14,0:09:32.48,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我要把那些家伙给烧了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.64,0:09:33.81,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,去把他们杀掉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.15,0:09:37.11,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 你太小看他们了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.61,0:09:39.61,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不要对漂流者掉以轻心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.65,0:09:43.57,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,下次我就会杀掉他们的 顺顺利利地把他们杀掉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.82,0:09:45.53,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我要去帮吉尔德莱报仇
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.53,0:09:46.12,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.49,0:09:49.79,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,等待时机
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.41,0:09:54.92,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,最后肯定会让你如意的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.84,0:09:59.96,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.38,0:10:04.43,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那个武士 要把他杀掉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.76,0:10:06.30,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,倾尽我全力地把他烧死
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.47,0:10:09.72,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我要把他烧得连炭都不剩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.81,0:10:12.77,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,她如何了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.31,0:10:14.94,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,总算是醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.14,0:10:17.98,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说头盖骨差点被掀开 但是很精神
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.31,0:10:20.77,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,黑王大人替她治好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.98,0:10:24.61,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不过在被带到这里之前死掉也毫不奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.74,0:10:28.74,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那个名为丰久的漂流者头目
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.03,0:10:32.75,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,貌似并不会因为对手是女人就手下留情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.75,0:10:35.46,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,手下留情了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.25,0:10:37.33,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我猜是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.13,0:10:39.25,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然手下留情了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.42,0:10:41.55,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不过那也是按照自己的标准行事而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.09,0:10:45.84,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,之后被手下留情的对象会变得怎样和他毫无关系
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.05,0:10:49.60,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,他的存在本身 就是自我满足的集合体啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.01,0:10:52.10,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是被称为武士的家伙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.43,0:10:54.56,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,就是如此 才无法让人小觑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.98,0:10:57.39,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,自那群家伙出现以来的800年间
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.69,0:11:01.52,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,他们就是在那狭小的岛国里不分昼夜地互相厮杀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.52,0:11:03.11,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,除此之外就无事可做的家伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.24,0:11:07.91,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,面对其末裔 我们俄罗斯不还是输了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.03,0:11:11.62,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,因为贞德被欺负所以生气了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.37,0:11:13.54,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,皇女大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.91,0:11:17.54,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,哪有生气
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.54,0:11:20.17,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,生气了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.17,0:11:28.26,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不要！快住手！不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.09,0:11:30.55,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,快停下来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.51,0:11:35.56,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,黑王 停下来 快让他们停下来！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.72,0:11:37.94,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,住手！让他们停下来！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.31,0:11:40.15,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,既然不愿和我们一伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.27,0:11:41.65,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你就只是块肉罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.74,0:11:50.07,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,给我闭上嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.87,0:12:02.63,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,哟 你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.50,0:12:05.84,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你是…哪边的？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.09,0:12:10.84,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那个公务员一样的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.05,0:12:13.43,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不就是个管理户口的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.60,0:12:16.64,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能赢得了我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.86,0:12:24.96,Drifters Normal,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.69,0:12:25.23,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？火枪？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.36,0:12:26.86,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,火枪是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.98,0:12:28.57,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,能吃么那个东西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.74,0:12:30.82,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,火枪啊 火枪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.03,0:12:33.78,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,他们这不是一直都在吃么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.03,0:12:36.54,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,老夫我们也想战斗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.95,0:12:39.08,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,再拿多点酒和饭菜过来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.83,0:12:42.29,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,吃了东西就太过精神了吧 你们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.29,0:12:44.84,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？要干架么 你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.29,0:12:44.84,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}啊？有意见么 你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.59,0:12:49.13,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这个工厂理应还有大量粮食的说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.38,0:12:51.34,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,居然会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.43,0:12:54.01,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,奥尔米小姐 有追加的吩咐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.01,0:12:55.55,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,一百人份量的汤
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.55,0:12:56.64,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么店啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.64,0:12:58.02,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,直接拿水给他们喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.48,0:13:04.36,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,他们越吃越壮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.19,0:13:10.94,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,好可怕 矮人果然很可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.16,0:13:14.70,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那算什么啊 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.28,0:13:17.08,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,夏拉 你为什么笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.20,0:13:20.00,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,矮人回归了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.12,0:13:22.87,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,睡前故事里面的矮人回归了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.59,0:13:28.55,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,噗哈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.00,0:13:30.38,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,噗哈你个头啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.67,0:13:33.65,Drifters Normal,,0,0,0,,那汤里不是有牛马的肉吗 这也吃得下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.01,0:13:37.07,Drifters Normal,,0,0,0,,在萨州 只要是肉都吃得下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.31,0:13:42.46,Drifters Normal,,0,0,0,,打仗时上顿不接下顿 饿起来连野狗也得吃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.11,0:13:44.42,Drifters Normal,,0,0,0,,{\an8}够了 你别说了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.27,0:13:54.24,Drifters Normal,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.27,0:13:50.82,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 听我说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.94,0:13:56.20,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那个叫义经的人真的是好过分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.28,0:13:59.24,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,在听么 老头子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.33,0:14:00.95,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我在听 我在听
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.04,0:14:08.25,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,本来 突然之间居然叫我射扇子什么的很奇怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.75,0:14:10.96,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,能中才怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.17,0:14:14.13,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,还叫我去射水手 是不是有病啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.43,0:14:18.35,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,还真是让人干不下去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.35,0:14:19.89,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,酒品还是差啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.06,0:14:22.22,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,会让人误会的 快把衣服穿好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.25,0:14:24.75,Drifters Normal,,0,0,0,,在萨州我也是这样喝的x
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.78,0:14:26.39,Drifters Normal,,0,0,0,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.66,0:14:31.57,Drifters Normal,,0,0,0,,老爷子 在吃什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.34,0:14:33.48,Drifters Normal,,0,0,0,,虫子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.64,0:14:34.32,Drifters Normal,,0,0,0,,{\an8}也给我们弄点酒来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.68,0:14:40.48,Drifters Normal,,0,0,0,,前略 织田家的各位身体还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.75,0:14:42.20,Drifters Normal,,0,0,0,,我是前右府
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.74,0:14:46.65,Drifters Normal,,0,0,0,,现在想起来 各位还真是听我的话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.69,0:14:47.85,Drifters Normal,,0,0,0,,你们真了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.15,0:14:50.40,Drifters Normal,,0,0,0,,但是光秀 你给我去死
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.84,0:14:54.19,Drifters Normal,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.55,0:14:57.47,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪里 把那个所谓的火枪给我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.68,0:14:58.80,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不要搞坏了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.89,0:15:00.30,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,才不会呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.93,0:15:08.44,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么 是铁筒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.60,0:15:10.98,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是把铁卷起来制造的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.19,0:15:14.69,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这个扳机的机关和弩有点像
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.82,0:15:16.74,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,真是简单
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.74,0:15:20.41,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这根铁棒会弹入这个圆盘中吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.45,0:15:22.12,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么目的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.24,0:15:24.08,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是射击用的装置么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.66,0:15:27.04,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,把手只是单纯的木头而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.58,0:15:31.59,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 这个到底是要怎么用的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.88,0:15:35.42,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 那个叫做火枪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.55,0:15:38.30,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,让火药在筒中炸裂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.43,0:15:40.64,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是可以让铅弹射出的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.72,0:15:42.93,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这是武器么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.51,0:15:45.60,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,射出铅弹？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.10,0:15:49.02,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不知道那个火药是什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.90,0:15:53.27,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要特意做些这么麻烦的事情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.48,0:15:56.19,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,弓和弩不是很好了么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.32,0:15:58.53,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,没有这个不行么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.86,0:16:01.99,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,关于这点我也是不清楚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.70,0:16:05.99,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,用弓的话既能无声无息地进攻又不用这样大费工夫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.12,0:16:08.16,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你要执着于火枪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.29,0:16:12.58,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 声音和硝烟也是必要的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.67,0:16:14.17,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么说才会好懂一点呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.42,0:16:17.13,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,枪火是火枪开枪时候的标志
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.46,0:16:20.38,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是你被瞄准了的信号
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.59,0:16:22.68,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,而且火枪的训练时间很短
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.84,0:16:26.77,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天还是农民的人 第二天甚至能打倒武士
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.64,0:16:31.19,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,果然 这家伙并非笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.35,0:16:33.31,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然是个专攻战斗的笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.11,0:16:36.94,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,远射程外加威力大
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.11,0:16:39.99,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,但是枪真正的优势并不全是这两点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.28,0:16:44.37,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,枪可以使杀人 杀意以及罪恶感简便化
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.91,0:16:48.33,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟只要轻轻扣动扳机 谁都能简单地成为士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.79,0:16:53.00,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那便是全民皆兵的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.38,0:16:57.13,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这可说不得 说不得
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.51,0:17:05.43,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,真有一手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.68,0:17:07.56,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.89,0:17:09.85,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你们的这个铁管啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.85,0:17:11.64,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是叫火枪什么的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.19,0:17:14.02,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你们国家的冶炼技术
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.06,0:17:16.32,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,勉强还是能说得上厉害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.86,0:17:19.65,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不过还是比不上我们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.15,0:17:21.70,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,拿去 第一根
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.99,0:17:25.24,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,什…喂 昨天才开始做
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.32,0:17:27.28,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,已经能做出来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.33,0:17:29.83,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,只有图纸的话还不好说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.91,0:17:31.62,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不过实物都摆在这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.71,0:17:34.25,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我们肯定能做出来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.46,0:17:35.58,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,快试试吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.79,0:17:38.05,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不过应该没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.09,0:17:43.34,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这个工房都市全力运转的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.05,0:17:46.30,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这东西能做出多少根来？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.39,0:17:50.89,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这个工房都市可是负责生产奥尔特一半以上的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.10,0:17:53.94,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这还是我们挨饿偷懒的结果
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.94,0:17:56.52,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我们动真格的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.15,0:18:01.61,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我想想 这跟剑和铠甲有很大区别
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.74,0:18:03.78,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然做熟手起来要花点时间
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.36,0:18:06.03,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,首先是七八根
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.20,0:18:09.08,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,然后会增加到十根左右吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.08,0:18:12.66,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,才这么点啊！亏你这么有自信
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.04,0:18:16.17,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,还不够吗？每天撑死十根
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.25,0:18:18.09,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,别强人所难了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.17,0:18:19.04,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,每天？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.54,0:18:22.88,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这矮人族真的假的 真心厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.84,0:18:26.34,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉摆出了一副阴险的表情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.34,0:18:30.35,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,他偶尔会这样 别管他就好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.47,0:18:34.56,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,丰久那边怎样了 还在吃他的饭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.77,0:18:36.35,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是去哪了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.56,0:18:39.27,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那个男的说要运动一下促进消化
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.31,0:18:42.82,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,带着我们的年轻人去了什么地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.82,0:18:47.20,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,说实话没法区分你们的年轻人和老家伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.41,0:18:49.41,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来全部都像大叔一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.53,0:18:50.70,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是因为什么诅咒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.70,0:18:51.70,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.87,0:18:58.38,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也能战斗！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.50,0:19:00.92,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,矮人族的战斗是一击必杀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.09,0:19:04.09,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是把一切都赌在这斧头上的一击的战法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.21,0:19:06.09,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,真是漂亮的破甲击
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.26,0:19:07.68,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,就像示现一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.88,0:19:10.72,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,示现…什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.76,0:19:15.18,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,示现流啊 御本家的年轻二子兴起的流派
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.31,0:19:17.23,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我只专注于体舍流
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.39,0:19:20.44,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么闲工夫去学什么示现流就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.77,0:19:25.44,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,即使位于遥远的世界也有同样的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.28,0:19:28.32,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,还真是有趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.86,0:19:30.74,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,就算身形外貌有区别
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.82,0:19:33.03,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,士兵可是在什么地方都会产生的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.41,0:19:34.87,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.91,0:19:36.87,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,什么时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.91,0:19:37.87,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.17,0:19:39.96,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不！你们是什么东西？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.08,0:19:44.13,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,继精灵族之后连矮人族也拉拢了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.38,0:19:47.51,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,漂流者们下手真是快呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.47,0:19:51.09,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然有想过这个可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.18,0:19:54.97,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,真的能让他们做出枪来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.18,0:19:57.85,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,多么令人毛骨悚然
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.98,0:19:59.02,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你是什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.06,0:20:00.52,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.02,0:20:03.02,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌 泥巴拍不下来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.15,0:20:05.61,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,大 大事不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.78,0:20:07.53,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,圣日耳曼的马车在外面…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.57,0:20:11.91,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人妖大领主伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.16,0:20:12.78,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.37,0:20:14.62,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你真失礼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.62,0:20:17.54,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,喂欧派米 这家伙是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.66,0:20:19.58,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是艺人吗 倒不如说是人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.83,0:20:21.29,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是圣日耳曼伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.46,0:20:24.54,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,支配着奥尔特三分之一土地的大贵族
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.71,0:20:26.42,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会在这
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.67,0:20:29.88,Drifters Normal,,0,0,0,,明明本大人特地大驾光临
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.88,0:20:34.10,Drifters Normal,,0,0,0,,结果你们从那废城出来之后迟迟不见回去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.41,0:20:37.01,Drifters Normal,,0,0,0,,等来等去也没有要回来的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.29,0:20:40.58,Drifters Normal,,0,0,0,,所以我才亲自跑到这脏乱差的地方来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.85,0:20:42.78,Drifters Normal,,0,0,0,,快感谢我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.51,0:20:43.89,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,圣日耳曼伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.97,0:20:46.85,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你有漂流者或者废弃物的嫌疑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.85,0:20:50.10,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,阿拉 说得人家像罪犯一样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.31,0:20:53.15,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,什么怀疑不怀疑 我就是漂流者
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.27,0:20:55.32,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会有我这样的废弃物啊 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.32,0:20:55.94,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.36,0:21:00.91,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,明明胸部很大 脑子却很轻呢你个笨女人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.03,0:21:05.24,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那为什么要和那个国父成立什么奥尔特帝国
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.45,0:21:06.62,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,真失礼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.70,0:21:08.79,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,奥尔特可了不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.87,0:21:11.50,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,别说得跟废弃物所作所为一样 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.79,0:21:14.25,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那位国父 阿道夫·希特勒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.25,0:21:15.92,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,也是货真价实的漂流者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.21,0:21:19.93,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,国父创建了高效的官僚主义帝国
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.05,0:21:23.93,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,把世袭的恶习连根拔起 分配了财富
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.22,0:21:27.64,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,然后又故意制造出「一定数量的差别阶级」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.72,0:21:31.44,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,以此来管理民众 完成中央集权
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.69,0:21:35.23,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,除了奖赏我的土地以外呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.32,0:21:37.78,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的工作可是十分出色的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.86,0:21:42.86,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不然如何能跟周围的种族打五十年仗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.03,0:21:46.45,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我之前见过和你有同样眼神的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.54,0:21:49.91,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,既不知道他是谁 也听不懂他在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.00,0:21:54.50,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙最后被茶壶里装满的火药给炸死了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.59,0:21:56.55,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,就是一种怪物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.76,0:22:00.55,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,松永弹正？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.76,0:22:00.55,Difters PS,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(763.2,17.4)}松永弹正：松永久秀，弹正为官位名。战国时期的武将，日本第一位自爆死的男子。
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.59,0:22:03.26,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 拿我和那种人比？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.39,0:22:05.10,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,真过分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.60,0:22:07.47,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙知道我们的事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.72,0:22:10.31,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙 不能放松警惕
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.68,0:22:13.60,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这位圣日耳曼伯爵到此有何贵干？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.44,0:22:18.48,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你们是否有资格和我联手 我来确认这一点了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.82,0:22:25.07,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是头目 岛津丰久吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.20,0:22:29.12,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 这家伙搞不懂到底是男是女
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.24,0:22:32.37,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你们是什么家伙 奥尔特的手下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.79,0:22:37.38,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 奥尔特的手下 就是这样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.46,0:22:38.63,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,现在还算
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.51,0:22:41.59,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,被看穿了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.92,0:22:44.97,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,剑很锐利 杀气却很钝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.09,0:22:46.01,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,有何企图
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.14,0:22:50.93,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,真可惜 再过个30年就是我喜欢类型
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.18,0:22:55.35,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不过没办法了 杀掉你的话就抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.52,0:22:58.69,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是身经百战的银发长者还糟糕点
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.82,0:23:01.44,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,你就怨恨自己的年轻去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.87,0:23:14.04,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,噢 老头子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.33,0:23:16.33,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 阿雷斯塔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.42,0:23:19.63,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 我不行了 站不起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.13,0:23:21.84,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,竟敢把阿雷斯塔…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.26,0:23:23.67,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我们什么都没做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.72,0:23:28.30,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 你和那老头都在我的射程外所以没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.93,0:23:31.97,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,要上了 我可不会输
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.02,0:23:35.81,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,只要不出来个遮住半边脸的单马尾少年！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.94,0:23:38.15,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,丰久殿下 大事不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.61,0:23:45.15,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,现在我手下的高手正在测试你们的头目
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.40,0:23:47.61,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 会变得如何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.61,0:23:51.91,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,公主大人… 救救我…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.54,0:23:55.00,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,想去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.37,0:23:57.12,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,啊丰久 什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.42,0:23:59.50,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不知道怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.63,0:24:01.00,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,就把他们揍了一顿
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.80,0:24:05.72,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,这儿也有个不知是男是女的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.97,0:24:06.97,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,来者何人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.55,0:24:09.68,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,卖国贼
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.93,0:24:11.22,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,卖国贼？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.30,0:24:15.85,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 我是到这来把奥尔特卖给你们的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.98,0:24:18.60,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,现在可是跳楼大甩卖哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.60,0:24:19.56,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,把国家…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.60,0:24:20.94,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,卖出去？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.11,0:24:22.90,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 要卖掉
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.98,0:24:25.86,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,趁现在还有点商品价值
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.03,0:24:29.16,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,就算要亡国 也有亡国的方式
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.24,0:24:33.62,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,是被诸国军队包围 在城下俯首称臣
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.70,0:24:38.00,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,国土四分五裂让人怎么受得了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.04,0:24:41.71,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,所以要让我们怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.38,0:24:44.96,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,趁奥尔特还存有力量
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.09,0:24:49.63,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,必须趁现在给奥尔特致命一击让其高效地崩溃
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.93,0:24:52.35,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,意下如何
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Drifters Normal,NTP,0,0,0,,---ed----
