Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.63,0:25:31.02,difters-ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}热浪就如晃荡的交响乐
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.23,0:25:41.03,difters-ed1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}その声は響く三日月を
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.23,0:25:41.03,difters-ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}那歌声 在新月之夜下荡漾
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.24,0:25:44.36,difters-ed1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}この身　焚べた炎
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.24,0:25:44.36,difters-ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}如此久久不息的火焰
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.53,0:25:46.83,difters-ed1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}明けぬ夜は無いと
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.53,0:25:46.83,difters-ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不存在永不破晓的黑夜
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.03,0:25:50.87,difters-ed1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}生を叫ぶ衝動 輝く
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.03,0:25:50.87,difters-ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}呼喊生存的冲动 闪耀着
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.95,0:25:56.04,difters-ed1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}Blaze your away 暁の空へ
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.95,0:25:56.04,difters-ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}开拓你的道路 向着拂晓之空
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.17,0:26:00.34,difters-ed1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}Bloodythirsty Noble Warriors
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.17,0:26:00.34,difters-ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}嗜血成性的高尚战士
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.42,0:26:05.09,difters-ed1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}赤く滲む痛み引き連れて
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.42,0:26:05.09,difters-ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}与被染红的痛楚一同
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.18,0:26:12.18,difters-ed1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}果てない今日を踏んだ大地へ
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.18,0:26:12.18,difters-ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}冲破无尽的今日 迈向新大陆
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.31,0:26:19.40,difters-ed1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}栄光を歌う peace at the end
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.31,0:26:19.40,difters-ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}歌颂荣光 终归和平
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.57,0:26:23.53,difters-ed1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}更なる大儀を掲げよう
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.57,0:26:23.53,difters-ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}高举更为雄壮的大义之旗
